name: ZecFi Capital
description: ZecFi was launched free and fair on pumpfun on 11/21/2025. It is a governance token tasked with governing a treasury funded by trading fees. All trading fees go towards buying assets, lending them, earning yield, and buying back zecfi from open market, reinforcing demand. That demand will increase trading volume, which will lead to more fees. A self sustaining lending protocol that is governed by its holders.
